{"tid":2099630,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"風向師真係連登最撚低賤嘅存在","createTime":"2020-07-08T11:16:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T09:36:46.000Z","uid":34572,"like":34,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f231a4a54cafa2848f3b53611646b124dd72b81b","tid":2099630,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T11:16:11.000Z","msg":"風向標永遠只能夠話俾人知宜家邊個方向嘅風最大，但從來都唔識話俾人知個風係颱風、係一般嘅陣風，定係人造出嚟嘅氣流。<br />\n<br />\n連登風向師就同風向標一樣，只係識得up邊個話題最多人講，唔駛深思背後原因同埋大家討論得合唔合理，只要係自己鍾意嘅話題冇人提，或者自己鍾意嘅人同物俾好多人屌，就會自動歸納為「有人帶風向」，繼而以此屈毛。呢啲人淨係識講咩嘢呢一刻多人講以去「報風向」，但完全冇思考過成因，亦冇能力分析，呢啲冇腦嘅on9仔比五毛更下賤。<br />\n<br />\n最後附上風向師老祖宗嘅經典<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Moup2s5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMoup2s5.jpg&h=a0b06802&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"227f225c4f50a8ba9c04d67ab56df5766ffc22b2","tid":2099630,"uid":38189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T11:32:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d36ff268198e74246563ed9795ee10b78fa8ac6f","tid":2099630,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T11:39:35.000Z","msg":"樓豬小氣師"},{"pid":"242c310fef7b14c4499e6843d01e6fbcdc3e0caa","tid":2099630,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T13:58:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46cafd65e02a348dd969bb4ffe06791b15645835","tid":2099630,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T13:59:40.000Z","msg":"樓主是PR, 拉"},{"pid":"a879c470172106109136edbc0a1c2a4dc0a747d3","tid":2099630,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T14:21:25.000Z","msg":"邊爐傑近排撈緊咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5805f8d19a42381eb3155f42274b5b33f9087bfe","tid":2099630,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a879c470172106109136edbc0a1c2a4dc0a747d3","tid":2099630,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0